channel.title: Strange problem with mopar forums
channel.description:
Hey guys,
I last logged on here about 2 weeks ago. But for some strange reason all the posts are exactly the same as when i logged off last time. The only way to find a recent post is search it. I've logged out and in and refreshed the page. And also i get the new posts in this section icon all the time so i enter that section and it's exactly the same as when i last checked. Also whenever i try and make a new topic it says "your session has timed out please repost" it only says it once in red writing then it lets me post. I'm freaking out big time guys. :P
All help is appreciated.
Thanx :)

item.title: Strange problem with mopar forums
